      <title>印度大选：莫迪联盟领先优势小于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-04/india-vote-modi-alliance-leads-count-with-tight-margin-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过六周的大选，印度仍在继续计票，纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的人民党联盟以低于预期的优势领先。哈斯琳达·阿明在新德里为彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-04/india-vote-modi-alliance-leads-count-with-tight-margin-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 07:18:23 GMT</pubDate>
